# AI features (photo import, URL fallback for sites without structured data,
# and AI suggestions for steps the rules can't map). The rules-based conversion
# and URL import work WITHOUT any of this — these just unlock the extras.
#
# Defaults target opencode Zen (https://opencode.ai/zen), an OpenAI-compatible
# gateway. Get a key at https://opencode.ai/auth. Any OpenAI-compatible gateway
# works by overriding AI_BASE_URL.

OPENCODE_ZEN_API_KEY=

# Optional overrides:
# AI_BASE_URL=https://opencode.ai/zen/v1
# AI_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5      # must be a model the gateway exposes; use a
#                                 # vision-capable one for photo import
